            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股午後窄幅  晶片股跌銀行股升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股收跌，午後窄幅疲軟，半導體股受壓，地方銀行股逆市升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-1-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指全日收報3342點，跌10點或0.3%，今早開報3350，跌2點0.06%，早段見3351點，跌1點或0.03%，為全日高位，隨即反覆向下，約11:AM見3335，跌17點或0.51%，為全日低位，午後窄幅，全日成交4648.62億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日報10126，跌70點或0.69%，今早開報10190，跌7點或0.07%，最高報10190，跌7點或0.07%，為全日高位，即拾級而下，最低報10087，跌110點或1.08%，為全日低位，午後波幅不超過上午，全日成交7271.48億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日報3846點，跌6點或0.17%，今早開報3848，跌4點或0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日跌17點或0.87%，報2011點，今早開報2028，跌1點或0.05%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">半導體多家股價調整，華虹公司(688347.SH)領跌，收報47.15元，挫9.33%；東土科技(300353.SZ)跌8.02%，報21.34元 ; 樂鑫科技(688018.SH)跌7.97%，報198.5元 ; 中芯(0688981.SH)跌4.61%，報85.83元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">銀行股集體走強，青島銀行(002144.SZ)升3.4%，報4.86元 ; 興業銀行(601166.SH)升2.65%，報22.1元 ; 重慶銀行(601963.SH)升2.96%，報7.65元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14915949-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e7%aa%84%e5%b9%85-%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 15:21:12",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "台積電4 月銷售按年增逾48%  關稅生效前企業爭相儲貨",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台積電4月銷售額3495.7億元(新台幣‧下同)，按月增加22.2％，按年增長48.1%，遠超分析師預期的38%，較上月46.5%的按年增速有所加快，按月則增22.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_TSMC-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_TSMC-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：台積電官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台積電首4個月累計銷售額為11888.21億元，按年增長43.5％，此前台積電公布的一季度凈利潤按年增60%超預期。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">電子企業在全球關稅生效前爭相採購關鍵零部件，台積電4月份營收大幅增長48%，不過新台幣的飆升可能會給台積電利潤率帶來壓力，台積電曾表示，新台幣每升值1%，其營業利潤率就會下降0.4個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14915782-%e5%8f%b0%e7%a9%8d%e9%9b%bb4-%e6%9c%88%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e%e9%80%be48-%e9%97%9c%e7%a8%85%e7%94%9f%e6%95%88%e5%89%8d%e4%bc%81%e6%a5%ad%e7%88%ad%e7%9b%b8%e5%84%b2%e8%b2%a8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230717-160018_20230717_fi_TSMC_fb_source-web_-1-1.jpg.webp",
